manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Featuring a curved screen, 4K SUHD resolution, and flexible connectivity options JS9100 Series 4K SUHD Smart TV At a Glance: Immerse yourself into the action w/ Curved Screen and Auto Depth Enhancer Outstanding brightness for viewing HDR content Featuring Peak Illuminator Pro Make your smart TV an instant pleasure w/ Octa Core Processing Brilliant color! With Nano Crystal technology get millions more colors than ever before Samsung JS9100 Series 4K SUHD Smart TV The Samsung JS9100 78-Inch 4K SUHD TV has an immersive curved screen, 4K UHD resolution, and Nano Crystal Color technology to provide a greater sense of depth and up to 64 times the color expression of a conventional HD/UHD TV.* Peak Illuminator Pro increases brightness for more detail, and the Precision Black feature improves contrast for more striking visuals. The octa-core processor, Samsung's highest grade processing chip, lets you alternate between media extremely quickly. Smart View 2.0 allows you to watch mobile media on your TV or vice versa, and with Motion Rate 240 you'll experience exceptional moving picture resolution. The included smart remote control has a built-in microphone that allows you to perform voice commands and a touchpad to navigate intuitively between menus. The One Connect Box helps you eliminate cable clutter by giving you a single, consolidated solution for all your audio and video connections. *Conventional HD/UHD TVs refer to 8-bit color TVs What's in the Box: Samsung JS9100 78-Inch 4K SUHD TV Smart remote control One Connect box

SUHD TV Delivers Incredible Color & Brightness With SUHD 4K TVs, now you can experience stunning colors, deep contrast, incredible brightness, and 4K resolution that redefines your TV viewing experience. Curved Screen Draws You into the Action Featuring a curved screen, the JS9100 SUHD TV creates an immersive viewing experience that is ideal for watching sports or movies. The screen's curved design provides a greater sense of depth and great off-angle viewing so every seat is the best seat in the house. Greater Contrast Depth with Auto Depth Enhancer The JS9100 SUHD TV also features Samsung contrast-enhancing technology, which optimizes contrast across multiple zones of the picture to produce a richer, more dramatic sense of depth. The technology deepens contrast without distorting the picture's color or detail, creating a more immersive and cinematic image.

Peak Illuminator Pro Enriches Color Content and Detail With the Samsung Peak Illuminator Pro feature, you'll experience brighter whites, sharper details, and more vibrant colors. This technology selectively adapts to each scene by intelligently brightening LED illumination behind the brightest regions of the picture. Precision Black Technology for Dramatic Contrast Equipped with Samsung Precision Black technology, the Samsung JS9100 SUHD TV delivers exceptional contrast depth. The TV deepens contrasts by selectively dimming LEDs behind the dark areas of the picture, thus making blacks darker without affecting the brighter elements in the picture. Motion Rate 240 Delivers Seamless Motion The JS9100 SUHD TV features a Motion Rate of 240 to ensure your TV keeps up with the action on-screen. With its outstanding refresh rate, processing speed and backlighting technology the JS9100 SUHD TV delivers a seamless moving image that renders fast action sequences easily.

Octa-Core Processor Delivers Rapid, Responsive Performance Equipped with the highest-grade processing chip from Samsung, the JS9100 Smart TV lets you switch between apps with ease. This powerful processor enables the TV to quickly respond to your commands, delivering a fluid experience. Smart View 2.0 for Easy Mobile Streaming Using the Samsung Smart View 2.0 feature, you can wirelessly share content between your TV and your mobile device.* *All devices must be on the same network and internet connection is required One Connect Box and Smart Remote Offer Streamlined Control The included One Connect Box helps you eliminate cable clutter by giving you a single, consolidated solution for all your audio and video connections. The included Smart Remote gives you optimized control over your Smart TV. Use the remote's touchpad to navigate intuitively between menus, or speak into the built-in microphone to perform voice commands.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Terrible tv and customer service
reviews.reviewText: Bought this tv June 2016 the screen went completely black on Saturday feb 4, 2017. THE DAY BEFORE THE SUPERBOWL. Today is feb,8th and I again had to call Samsung and ask when will my tv be repaired. Again I was told I will get a call in the next 48 hours to schedule my service. I have done the online chat, I have emailed, and I have called on the telephone. THE WORST CUSTOMER SERVICE.... I would expect a $5000.00 tv to last longer than a few months and I certainly expect much better customer service. If you are buying a tv and its a toss up between Samsung and another maker. Pick the other maker.Update: April 5th. Samsung picked up my TV today, because they don't have a certified tech in my area. I now have the choice of a refurbished TV or a refund. Chose the refund, after many calls. I was told the check would be mailed after the condition of the tv was verified. The worst customer service I have ever experienced !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 13, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars This is really a fantastic set up
reviews.reviewText: This is really a fantastic set up, especially to offer 4k. Picture is very clear and no freeze or motion rate issues at all. Really enjoying it and no service or picture issues at all. Recommendation is to ensure you are getting the correct panel edition, as they make the "demo" version (Costco) and the real quality version. TS01, TH01 or a TH02 version Panels are what you want for best picture quality.

reviews.reviewText: I have a bunch tvs & they keep losing their connection to Smartthings. I've been in touch with Samsung many times and they make me reconnect the TV and the problem persists. Now the police gave me a ticket because the TV does not shut off after Sunset and I'm bothering the turtles on the beach! What is the use of having a smart house when it's so dumb?
